## 完整描述 / Full Description
（4000字以内）

**英文：**

Star Park is an interactive growth and educational application designed for children. Using the gentle and soothing tones of the ancient Chinese instrument — the Guqin — as the auditory core, it helps children develop daily habits, cultivate calm focus, and express their emotions in a positive way.

🎵 Three Core Music Modules

• Association — 15 carefully curated Guqin pieces guide children through sensory awakening, social connection, and personal growth. Each piece is paired with beautiful visual imagery and gentle prompts to stimulate imagination and emotional resonance.

• Recall — Children listen to Guqin music while parents record reflections and upload personalized images. A 60-second listening timer encourages sustained attention and peaceful engagement.

• Meditation — A candlelight focus experience with Mountain and Earth tone paths. Children earn puzzle rewards for sustained mindfulness: 1 minute (+1), 5 minutes (+2), 10 minutes (+3).

🌟 Achievement Reward System

Five interactive reward collections motivate continued participation:

🔵 Association Sparks

🐾 Recall Forest Prints

🧩 Meditation Puzzles

🪨 Sensory Foundation Stones

💧 Habit Droplets

🧠 Sensory & Interactive Training

16 structured sensory activities across social, visual, motor, tactile, auditory, and emotional domains. Designed especially for children aged 1–3, supporting eye contact, response to cues, physical coordination, fine motor skills, and social greetings.

✅ Habit Building

Four daily routines with clear visual task cards to build independence:

Toilet Training

Self-Dressing

Morning Hygiene

Independent Eating

Each completed task earns a star. Complete all four routines to unlock the Ultimate Star Award!

📊 Emotion & Attention Tracking

Built-in wellness check records children's mood before and after each session using a friendly 5-point emoji scale (Sad → Joyful) and a 3-level focus rating (Drifting → Focused). Data is visualized in the Progress Report.

👨‍👩‍👧 Parent Dashboard

Daily and lifetime achievement overview

Animated bar charts tracking progress across all 5 modules

Behavioral observation log with mood transition tracking

Bilingual support (Chinese / English)

🌍 Multilingual Support

Full support for Chinese, English, and Spanish across all modules.

🔒 Privacy & Safety

All session data is stored locally or anonymized, identified only by a randomly generated device ID

No personal information collected

COPPA compliant — designed for supervised use by parents and caregivers

No advertisements

About the Guqin

The Guqin is one of China's oldest musical instruments, with over 3,000 years of history. Its deep, resonant, and natural tones promote relaxation, mental clarity, and emotional balance — making it an ideal companion for early childhood development.

Star Park bridges ancient musical wisdom with modern developmental guidance, offering families a gentle, beautiful tool to support their child's daily growth.

中文：

星园是一款专为儿童设计的互动成长与美育启蒙应用。本应用以中国传统古琴优雅、宁静的自然音色为核心，帮助孩子在优美的琴声中培养专注力、引导健康情绪，并轻松建立良好的每日生活习惯。

🎵 三大核心音乐模块

• 联想 — 15首精心编排的古琴曲目，引导孩子经历感官觉醒、社交连接和人格成长三个阶段。每首曲目配有唯美的视觉图像和温和的引导语，激发想象力与情感共鸣。

• 回想 — 孩子聆听古琴音乐的同时，家长记录成长感悟并上传个性化图片。60秒专注计时解锁上传功能，鼓励孩子保持耐心与投入。

• 冥想 — 温暖的烛光专注体验，分高山和大地两条音调路径。孩子通过持续专注获得拼图奖励：坚持1分钟（+1）、5分钟（+2）、10分钟（+3）。

🌟 成就奖励系统

五大趣味奖励收集，激励孩子持续探索：

🔵 联想火花

🐾 回想森林爪印

🧩 冥想拼图

🪨 感统基石

💧 习惯水滴

🧠 感统与互动训练

16项结构化趣味感统互动，涵盖社交、视觉、运动、触觉、听觉和情绪引导领域。特别适合1-3岁幼儿，支持眼神交流、呼唤反应、平衡协调、精细动作和基本社交礼仪。

✅ 习惯养成

四大每日生活习惯，配有生动的视觉任务卡，培养独立自主能力：

独立如厕

自主穿衣

洗漱清洁

独立进餐

每完成一项任务获得一颗星，四项全部完成解锁终极小明星奖励！

📊 情绪与注意力追踪

内置情绪看板，使用5级表情量表（难过→开心）记录每次练习前后的心情状态，配合3级注意力评分（游离→专注）。数据自动同步并在成长报告中直观展示。

